1
00:00:04,820  --> 00:00:06,940
It must be tiring for you.
肯定让你身心俱疲

2
00:00:12,560  --> 00:00:14,640
Well, I admire your strength.
我欣赏你的坚强

3
00:00:15,100 --> 00:00:17,700
I know it must be hard for you to be strong all the time for these girls.
我知道在这些女生面前一直故作坚强一定很辛苦

4
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:21,640
You know, they're lucky to have a woman such as yourself to keep going for all of them.
能有你这样的女人来维持学校是她们的幸运

5
00:00:29,260  --> 00:00:31,980
They can't know what it's like out there.
她们不可能知道外面的情形

6
00:00:42,280  --> 00:00:44,760
There's no sense to be made of it.
没什么能理解的

7
00:00:47,020  --> 00:00:49,480
Did you have someone before the war?
你在战前有爱人吗

8
00:01:00,860  --> 00:01:02,660
Well, I'm sorry.
对不起

9
00:01:07,360  --> 00:01:09,660
I was a coward to leave,
之前 我像个懦夫一样离开了

10
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:13,640
but you don't realize what battle really is until you've seen it.
但是只有亲眼看到 你才会知道战场是什么样子

11
00:01:22,420 --> 00:01:23,320
I had nothing.
一无所有

12
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:27,440
I took 300 dollars to take another man's place.
我收了三千美金 替另一个人当兵